2) Once installed, change the name of "Cuestation" into "SpaceMap"... \
3) To learn how to create maps, check Meyer Sound Dimitri tutorials for Spacemap.\
4) Once you have saved and named your map, use Spacemap 2 Json.maxpat to change the dimitriproject into a json file, which the MIAP object understands. The map you created will be in the "parsed maps" folder.\
